column5: And I feel so GGGOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOODDDDDDDDDDDD.  Just need a new cranking battery.  ZOOM ZOOM ZOOM
I just got mine now I have to find all the pieces and put it back together still tons of ice up near port bolster
I got mine last night....  We are talking about the same thing right? Where's the cranking battery go?
I think thees guys are talking about Metamucil or all bran?
It's been a while but I think I did...  Can't imagin forgetting sumpin' like that...
Does this thing vibrate or somethin?  Rob C
mail order brides?  .... sounds like some folks got their boats out of storage and good thing you said ZOOM ZOOM ZOOM misfish, hear ZOOM ZOOM is patented by mazda

Thank you for this bud................................................................   To know me! I am a fisherman for life. I will always be a fisherman. It's not something I do; it's who I am. Fishing is not an escape. It is where I belong, where I am supposed to be. It is not a place, but a life long journey. It is a passage my grandfather showed me, and I will show others. When you understand all of this, You will know me, and we will fish together.
Well said!!!  That should be on a card or something  Don
i stumbled across it on the net somewhere, and i have no clue where i got it from...  it's like a fishermens prayer almost... seems suitable for most guys here!!
